Indian high court website do not provide an easy way interface to download
judgments. The major problems are discussed
http://lawandotherthings.blogspot.com/2009/02/e-legal-government-efforts-shortcomings.html.
This project aims to circumvent those problems by reverse engineering these
websites and providing an easy interface for downloading court judgments.

These scripts use the date search form for downloading judgments.

You will need python for these scripts. And they are tested only on Gnu/Linux.
